25d34bc7-a849-5572-8bc5-d14bfe4efdf2,tg:rubgr:4561,e73_Descriptions,,id.desc,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,"Connections between Bosch & Bruegel in Vienna Last Judgment: 1) Rebel Angels; 2) Central picture-composition: Proverbs (Stridbeck); 3) Many details of Hell in centre recur in drawings of Deadly Sins (examine in detail); 4) Last Judgment above cf. drawing of Last Judgment: the grouping of figures; 5) Ira (Baldass 1959, pl. 44)[= Hieronimus Bosch, Wien: Schroll, 1959] group of soldiers, one with helmet, cf. column4: <content>Connections between Bosch & Bruegel in Vienna Last Judgment: 1) Rebel Angels; 2) Central picture-composition: Proverbs (Stridbeck); 3) Many details of Hell in centre recur in drawings of Deadly Sins (examine in detail); 4) Last Judgment above cf. drawing of Last Judgment: the grouping of figures; 5) Ira (Baldass 1959, pl. 44)[= Hieronimus Bosch, Wien: Schroll, 1959] group of soldiers, one with helmet, cf. Bruegel: Fall of Rebel Angels.</content>
